Articles.Content:
I'm Playing RO/RP-0 and I've run into a small snag. I'm not sure where the issue lies, but it looks as though the Keybinding for B9 Procedural Wings inside the VAB doesn't do anything. I'm assuming there's a conflict with another mod that's preventing the UI to change the parameters of the wings from displaying, but I'm not sure how to pinpoint the issue. 

Any advice would be greatly appreciated

Can't delete posts.. I installed the Legacy Version of B9, not the new fork. Put the Fork at https://github.com/Crzyrndm/B9-PWings-Fork/releases in it's place and now I can make pretty wingys 

Edited April 23, 2017 by PsyberMind
